descriptionHtml:
A New Island Is Added To The Game Including: 

A Town, With Its Own Guard System. 
7 New Merchants. 
A New Follower. 
A Temple Of Talos. 
An Armory. 
A Golden Glow Estate Style Player Home. 
3 Trainers To Train You In The 3 Main Skills Of The Ranger. 
A Barracks. 
An Inn. 
A New Armor Set. 
New Weapons. 
New Npc's. 
A Working Jail. 
Multiple Shops. 
And More! 

The Boat To The Island Can Be Found In The Solitude Docks, Just InFront Of The Stairs, Just Activate The Statue Ontop Of The Wheel And You Will Be Transported To Ranger Isle. May Be More Updates Soon. Please Rate And Subscribe For More Mods! Please Comment Some Suggestions For My Next Mods! Thanks!!
